# Big-DB artifacts that are regenerated locally and not committed directly:
#
# - `anydice-programs-all.db`        Uncompressed (1.1GB). Inflate from .db.gz via
#                                    `gunzip --keep anydice-programs-all.db.gz`.
# - `anydice-programs-all.db.gz`     Reassembled from shards via
#                                    `assemble-programs-db.sh`. The shards
#                                    (anydice-programs-all.db.gz.part-*.bin) are
#                                    the canonical source-of-truth in this repo.
# - `anydice-programs-all-*.db.gz`   Timestamped pack snapshots produced locally by
#                                    `pack-programs-db.sh`; provenance archives for
#                                    the maintainer's working tree, not committed.
#
# The small DB (anydice-programs.db.gz + timestamped form + .sha256) IS committed
# directly because it fits comfortably under GitHub's per-file limits.
/anydice-programs-all.db
/anydice-programs-all.db.gz
/anydice-programs-all-*.db.gz
